if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('base_country')
and type = 'U')
drop table base_country
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: base_country */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_country (
CountryID int identity,
CnName nvarchar(100) not null,
EnName nvarchar(100) not null,
moneytype nvarchar(20) null,
Description nvarchar(500) null,
AddTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
constraint PK_BASE_COUNTRY primary key (CountryID)
)
go
